{"tid":804860,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"八大學生衣著樣貌排名","createTime":"2018-09-03T10:42:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-03T12:01:27.000Z","uid":104330,"like":1,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"de32d7ffafda0854c18c6968ebf26a7d821ebe64","tid":804860,"uid":104330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T10:42:23.000Z","msg":"衣著：poly&gt;cityu&gt;&gt;&gt;HKU&gt;&gt;&gt;BU&gt;&gt;UST&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;CU&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;lingu/edu<br />\n<br />\n樣貌：<br />\nCityu&gt;&gt;HKU/Polyu&gt;&gt;&gt;UST&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;CU/BU&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;lingu/edu<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 著得好睇同埋講靚仔靚女多就一定係九龍個兩間mk大學架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nPoly仔個個著衫都好有taste又有特色，唔計少部份毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> city仔就雖然好mk 但勝在個樣襯到佢地套mk韓仔風 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 港大就真係sell blue blood 有好靚好型 但同時有死讀書毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 無咩中間好睇既人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 科大都係 高質真係幾好屌 但無奈地成班毒撚仔仔扣撚哂分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 中大係山區 山區兒童唔多打扮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 浸大就唔多出名 印象普通<br />\n<br />\n最後個兩間 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  人太少 少高質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c345ef6240def00daa3b9661f37888bb8fa67e3","tid":804860,"uid":204700,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T10:44:55.000Z